64eac74c-d5fc-4c83-bc79-9d2b04f2dd70.name: DigADiscTrench
64eac74c-d5fc-4c83-bc79-9d2b04f2dd70.python_code:
def DigADiscTrench(self, radius, width, depth):
    self.action_implementer.create_digital_disc(normal_vec3=(Vec3(0, 1, 0)), center_point_vec3=(self.action_implementer.mcplayer.here - Vec3(0, (math.ceil(depth / 2 - 1)), 0)), outer_radius=radius, block_type='PACKED_ICE', disc_thickness=depth, inner_radius=(radius - width))

fb060ad9-2902-4ce3-94a2-c5dd93febfc1.name: MakeADiscWall
fb060ad9-2902-4ce3-94a2-c5dd93febfc1.python_code:
def MakeADiscWall(self, center_point, radius, width, depth, material):
    self.action_implementer.create_digital_disc(normal_vec3=(Vec3(0, 1, 0)), center_point_vec3=(center_point + Vec3(0, (math.ceil(depth / 2 - 1)), 0)), outer_radius=radius, block_type=material, disc_thickness=depth, inner_radius=(radius - width))

def MakeALine(self, point_a, Point_b, material):
